»SML:          »CL9:-----      --------------------------------------      -----
                                »CL4:By Cytron/Depth


»CL8:This Easter a German party, the
»CL4:Symposium Mekka» is held in a small
German town called »CL4:Fallingbostel.»
Travelling down here by train, one
quickly gets the expectation that the
party will be held in a »CL4:small barn» in
a »CL5:huge »CL4:German forest. »CL8:This is luckily
not the case. Actually, the party
takes place in a nice tempered hall
with room for about »CL4:500 people». And
500 people have definately come to
this place to have a good time.
Furthermore - about 7 »CL4:drunken Germans»







have met up to break some bottles and
make a lot of noice. But in my opinion
the organizers are handling things
well until now. I've only been here
for about twelve hours, but I really
feel that this party is a nice one and
I think that the compos will be great.
Unlike many parties of today, I don't
feel that the mood of the party is
sitting in front of a screen playing
»CL4:doom» or watching some »CL4:Mpegs» or
whatever. 

»PIC:DrZulu2»



















