   »CL8:The people that have showed up are
   mainly Germans of course, but I'd
   say that about »CL4:20 Danes» have met up
   as well. Other minorities present
   are the C64-owners. I've seen about
   »CL4:5 C64's». And frankly - the amiga is
   getting to be a minority as well.
   The Amiga/PC ratio is as low as
   »CL5:1:3». However, as I've said before,
   this doesn't seem to affect a
   generally »CL4:cozy» and »CL4:relaxed party-
   mood». All in all, my general
   impressions of this party so far
   are of »CL4:positive» kind. Hope to see
   you next year - in a small barn in
   Germany :-)  